/-
A tactic which constructs exprs to discharge
goals of the form `clauses.unsat cs`.
-/
theorem forall_mem_replicate_zero_eq_zero (m : nat) : ∀ x ∈ list.replicate m (0 : int), x = (0 : int) := fun x =>
  list.eq_of_mem_replicate
#align forall_mem_replicate_zero_eq_zero forall_mem_replicate_zero_eq_zero
